# --- Build & Dependency Artifacts ---
# Exclude these to prevent the AI from indexing thousands of library files
**/node_modules/
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.angular/

# --- IDE & System ---
.git/
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store

# --- AI Chat History ---
# Critical for token savings: Exclude past chat logs to prevent context window bloat
copilot/copilot-conversations/

# --- Logs & Temporary Files ---
**/coverage/
*.log
*.tmp

# --- Large Media/Binaries ---
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.mp4
*.svg
*.pdf
*.zip

# --- Exceptions: Allow Course Screenshots ---
# Allow AI to see diagrams/slides in the Resources folder for Course Scribe
!03_Resources/**/*.png
!03_Resources/**/*.jpg
!03_Resources/**/*.jpeg